I"d<p><strong>Science Pulse</strong> is a project led by ICFJ Knight Fellow Sérgio Spagnuolo in collaboration with <a href="https://voltdata.info">Volt Data Lab</a>, a data-driven news agency he founded in Sao Paulo, Brazil. It is supported by the <a href="https://icfj.org">International Center for Journalists (ICFJ)</a> and by the Brazilian science journalism agency <a href="https://abori.com.br/">Bori</a>.</p>

<p><small>You can find our privacy policy and license <a href="../privacy">in this link</a>.</small> <small>Read about the methodology <a href="../eng/methodology">here</a>.</small></p>

<p><a href="https://www.icfj.org/" target="_blank"><img src="https://sciencepulse.org/img/icfj.png" alt="logo ICFJ" width="160px" style="padding-right:8px" /></a>
